FBIS4-49865 "drchi091_n_94011" FBIS-CHI-94-091 Daily Report 10 May 1994 Economic & Agricultural Small, Medium-Sized Firms' Goods `Low Quality' Small, Medium-Sized Firms' Goods `Low Quality' HK1105072694 Beijing ZHONGGUO XINWEN SHE in English 1325 GMT 10 May 94 HK1105072694 Beijing ZHONGGUO XINWEN SHE English BFN [Text] Beijing, May 10 (CNS) -- The State Bureau of Technological Supervision has found the quality of products of large-sized enterprises improved but those from medium- and small-scale and township enterprises were still producing counterfeit and low quality products. Some 954 of medium and small-sized enterprises were examined, making up 82.5 percent of the total enterprises looked at. Of these, only 63.7 percent of the products were found to meet the standards and only 62.7 percent of township enterprise products were found to meet the standards, and at the same time, the production of counterfeit and low quality products remained serious.
